174 A.3d 516 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. SCHYLER A. MAY A/K/A SCHYLER ANTHONY MAY, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-151 September Term 2017

079289 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000692-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
